# Colang 2.0 — Content Safety Flow

define user ask harmful content
  "how to make a bomb"
  "how to hack into"
  "how to create a virus"
  "how to make weapons"
  "how to synthesize drugs"
  "how to exploit vulnerabilities"

define flow content safety
  user ask harmful content
  bot refuse harmful

define bot refuse harmful
  "I cannot provide information on harmful or illegal activities. This request has been blocked by our content safety guardrails."
